'''方舟投资'''，全称'''方舟投资管理有限责任公司'''（{{lang-en|ARK Investment Management LLC}}），是一家总部位于美国纽约[[资产管理|资产管理]]公司，由[[凯瑟琳·伍德|凯瑟琳·伍德]]于2014年创建。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Fitzgerald |first=Maggie |date=2020-12-23 |title=Cathie Wood's Ark Innovation becomes largest actively managed ETF, amid 170% 2020 return |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/12/22/ark-innovation-becomes-largest-actively-managed-etf-as-innovation-hits-escape-velocit.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119123217/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/12/22/ark-innovation-becomes-largest-actively-managed-etf-as-innovation-hits-escape-velocit.html |archive-date=2021-01-19 |access-date=2021-01-20 |website=CNBC |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Cuccinello |first=Hayley C. |title='Go For It': America's Richest Self-Made Women On Founding Businesses After 40 |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/hayleycuccinello/2020/10/13/american-self-made-women-founders-over-40/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119075323/https://www.forbes.com/sites/hayleycuccinello/2020/10/13/american-self-made-women-founders-over-40/ |archive-date=2021-01-19 |access-date=2021-01-20 |website=Forbes |language=en}}</ref>截至2021年2月，该公司管理大约500亿美元资产。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2020-02-05 |title=Cathie Wood Amasses $50 Billion and a New Nickname: ‘Money Tree’ |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-05/cathie-wood-amasses-50-billion-and-a-new-nickname-money-tree |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219000856/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-05/cathie-wood-amasses-50-billion-and-a-new-nickname-money-tree |archive-date=2021-02-19 |access-date=2021-02-20 |language=en}}</ref>

== 投资策略 ==
方舟投资关注那些应用革命性技术的公司。<ref>{{Cite news |date=2020-12-31 |title=The Best Stock Picker of 2020 Wins With Disruptive DNA |language=en |work=Bloomberg.com |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-12-31/ark-s-cathie-wood-bets-on-dna-innovators |access-date=2021-01-20 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204222954/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=81135750-6738-11eb-977d-3559f3773b55&url=L29waW5pb24vYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAyMC0xMi0zMS9hcmstcy1jYXRoaWUtd29vZC1iZXRzLW9uLWRuYS1pbm5vdmF0b3Jz |dead-url=no }}</ref>这类科技包括[[人工智能|人工智能]]、[[DNA測序|DNA測序]]、基因编辑、机器人、电动车、[[储能技术|储能技术]]、[[金融科技|金融科技]]、[[3D打印|3D打印]]、[[区块链|区块链]]、[[加密货币|加密货币]]等。该公司也会向公众发布行情分析、交易、投资组合以及研究报告。<ref>{{Cite news |date=2020-09-26 |title=Secret Sauce Behind Ark's Success Is Cathie Wood's Diverse Team |language=en |work=Bloomberg.com |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-09-26/secret-sauce-behind-ark-success-is-cathie-wood-s-diverse-team |access-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120201520/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-09-26/secret-sauce-behind-ark-success-is-cathie-wood-s-diverse-team |archive-date=2020-11-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Management |first=ARK Investment |title=ARK Investment Management LLC Celebrates Five Years Of Disruptive Innovation Investing |url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/ark-investment-management-llc-celebrates-five-years-of-disruptive-innovation-investing-300783457.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204222942/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/ark-investment-management-llc-celebrates-five-years-of-disruptive-innovation-investing-300783457.html |archive-date=2021-02-04 |access-date=2021-01-20 |website=www.prnewswire.com |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Alster |first=Norm |date=2020-10-08 |title=A New Kind of Fund That Is Stingier With Information |language=en-US |work=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/article/etf-funds.html |access-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129123708/https://www.nytimes.com/article/etf-funds.html |archive-date=2021-01-29 |issn=0362-4331}}</ref>

从2014年至2021年，该公司的方舟创新ETF（{{lang|en|ARK Innovation ETF}}）达到39%的年回报率，超过同期[[标准普尔500指数|标准普尔500指数]]的增长。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news |last=Zweig |first=Jason |date=2021-02-05 |title=Cathie Wood Has Wall Street's Hottest Hand. Maybe Too Hot. |language=en-US |work=Wall Street Journal |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/cathie-wood-is-wall-streets-hottest-hand-maybe-too-hot-11612544044 |access-date=2021-02-06 |issn=0099-9660 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317084531/https://www.wsj.com/articles/cathie-wood-is-wall-streets-hottest-hand-maybe-too-hot-11612544044 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==旗下ETF==
===主动管理型===
* ARK'''F'''–Fintech Innovation ETF：投资金融科技领域的创新型公司
* ARK'''G'''–Genomic Revolution ETF： 投资基因治疗，分子医疗和制药领域的创新型公司
* ARK'''K'''–ARK Innovation ETF：投资跨行业的创新型公司
* ARK'''Q'''–ARK Autonomous Tech. & Robotics ETF：投资机器人技术，自动驾驶汽车，能源存储，3D打印和太空探索领域的创新型公司
* ARK'''W'''–ARK Next Generation Internet ETF：投资云计算，大数据，数字媒体，电子商务，区块链技术和物联网领域的创新型公司
* ARK'''X'''–Space Exploration & Innovation ETF：投资於「引領、賦能或受益於地球表面以外的技術賦能產品、服務」的國內外公司，包括軌道航空航天、亞軌道航空航天、賦能技術、航空航天受益者的创新型公司

===指數型===
* IZRL – ARK Israel Innovative Technology：以色列创新指数基金, 旨在追踪主要业务运营在以色列交易所上市的以色列公司的价格走势, 包括:（i）健康技术，（ii）通信，（iii）技术服务，（iv）电子技术，（v）消费者服务
* PRNT – The 3D Printing ETF：3D 打印指数基金, 旨在追踪参与3D打印行业的公司的股票价格走势, 包括:（i）3D打印硬件，（ii）计算机辅助设计（CAD）和3D打印模拟软件，（iii）3D打印中心，（iv）扫描和测量，以及（v）3D打印材料

